data.description:
Fabulous two-story condominium in Glendale is now on the market! Upon arrival, you will be greeted by a charming courtyard where you can sit & enjoy the peaceful neighborhood. Inside, you'll find a merged living/dining room designed to maximize space for a seamless connection to everyday living. Cook your favorite meals in this galley kitchen, boasting ample cabinets, granite counters, built-in appliances, and recessed lighting. Continue upstairs to discover two primary bedrooms, each w/its own balcony access, walk-in closet, & private bathroom. Additional storage is no problem, thanks to the built-in cabinets in the garage. Imagine starting your day sipping coffee on the relaxing balcony overlooking the lovely community. 
**Seller to pay up to $4500.00 towards buyer's closing costs.
